    <body>
      <div xml:id="NA140-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">itu kuṟai (G1+2: vāyiṉ) maṟukkappaṭṭa talaivaṉ taṉ ṉeñciṉai neruṅkiyatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">This is how HE who had [his] requests refused addresses [his] own heart.</p>
      </div>
      <div xml:id="NA140">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            koṇṭaṉ māmaḻai kuṭakkērpu kuḻaitta</l>
<l>            ciṟukō liṇara peruntaṇ cāntam</l>
<l>            vakaicē raimpāṟ kaipeṟa vārip</l>
<l>            pularviṭat tutirtta tukaḷpaṭu kūḻaip</l>
<l>            peruṅkaṇ ṇāya muvappat tantai </l>
<l>            neṭuntēr vaḻaṅku nilavumaṇaṉ muṟṟattup</l>
<l>            pantoṭu peyarum parivi lāṭṭi</l>
<l>            yaruḷiṉu maruḷā ḷāyiṉum peritaḻintu</l>
<l>            piṉṉilai muṉiyaṉmā neñcē yeṉṉatūu</l>
<l>            maruntuya ravalan tīrkku </l>
<l>            maruntupiṟi tillaiyā ṉuṟṟa nōykkē.</l>
            </lg>
       <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Whether she has consideration or whether she has no consideration,</l>
<l>the emotionless woman who moves with a ball over the expanse</l>
<l rend="indent3">of moonlit sand, where the long chariot of [her] father wanders,</l>
<l rend="indent2">so that [her] large-eyed companions rejoice, with short hair,</l>
<l rend="indent2">into which the big cool sandal in small-stemmed bunches,</l>
<l rend="indent">that sprouted when great clouds had risen to the west with the east wind,</l>
<l rend="indent2">is combed to achieve by hand the five-parted [hairstyle] joined</l>
<l rend="indent2">after a fashion [and] becomes dust that dropped in places</l>
<l rend="indent3">where it is dry(?),</l>
<l>don't feel disgust, great heart, for standing behind [her], greatly desolate.</l>
<l>There is not other remedy</l>
<l rend="indent3">that ends the affliction of difficult misery at all,</l>
<l rend="indent4">for the pain I had.</l>
        </lg>
         </div>
